OL,3,CCouncil takes back control of some
OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council is taking
OL,7,Fback control of some sport services
OL,8,Ffrom Live Borders, the charity
OL,9,Fdelivering sport, leisure and cultural
OL,10,Fservices on the authorities behalf.
OL,12,FThe charity has been experienced
OL,13,Ffinancial problems since the Covid
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FAt a meeting on 27 July 2024, elected
OL,17,Fmembers decided that the Active
OL,18,FSchools and sports development
OL,19,Fservices will return under council
OL,20,Fcontrol.
