OL,6,FThe charity has faced unprecedented
OL,7,Fchallenges, including the Covid
OL,8,Fpandemic, cost of living and changes
OL,9,Fin customer trends.
OL,11,FThe charity says it has invested
OL,12,Fmillions of pounds from its financial
OL,13,Freserves into sustaining services,
OL,14,Ffacilities and equipment.
OL,16,FThey have also recieved millions of
OL,17,Fpounds of funding from the Council to
OL,18,Fkeep services running.
