OL,6,FDavid Robertson, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FScottish Borders Council, said: "It
OL,8,Fwas clear prior to the joint review
OL,9,Fthat changes were required to help
OL,10,FLive Borders get on a sustainable
OL,11,Ffooting and protect the continued
OL,12,Fdelivery of key services to our
OL,13,Fresidents and visitors.
OL,15,F"We are committed to working closely
OL,16,Fwith the Live Borders board and our
OL,17,Fcolleagues to ensure a seamless
OL,18,Ftransition to the new operating model.
